## A. 궁금해

12wk-2 강의노트중.. 

::: {#fdf90cc9-8ea5-4126-b3a3-4c347434fde2 .cell tags='[]' execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
df_sample = pd.DataFrame(
    {'path':['A','A','B','B','B'],
     'lon':[-73.986420,-73.995300,-73.975922,-73.988922,-73.962654],
     'lat':[40.756569,40.740059,40.754192,40.762859,40.772449]}
)
fig = px.line_mapbox(
    data_frame=df_sample,
    lat = 'lat',
    lon = 'lon',
    color = 'path',
    line_group = 'path',
    #---#
    mapbox_style = 'carto-positron',
    zoom=12,
    width = 750,
    height = 600    
)
scatter_data = px.scatter_mapbox(
    data_frame=df_sample,
    lat = 'lat',
    lon = 'lon',
    color = 'path',
    #---#
    mapbox_style = 'carto-positron',
    zoom=12,
    width = 750,
    height = 600    
).data 
fig.add_trace(scatter_data[0])
fig.add_trace(scatter_data[1])
fig.show(config={'scrollZoom':False})
```

